# .dockerignore
#
# Fallback ignore rules applied when no Dockerfile-specific .dockerignore exists.
# The production build uses Dockerfile.dockerignore instead (which also excludes
# test/). This file covers only credentials and OS artifacts that should never
# be in any image.

# Credentials — never bake these in; bind-mount at runtime instead
.env

# Git history
.git
.gitattributes

# Editor and OS artifacts
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
Thumbs.db
